{"id":40532,"date":"2023-03-15T20:49:13","date_gmt":"2023-03-15T19:49:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/care4calais.org\/?p=40532"},"modified":"2023-03-16T20:50:03","modified_gmt":"2023-03-16T19:50:03","slug":"please-join-us-at-the-demo","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/care4calais.org\/news\/please-join-us-at-the-demo\/","title":{"rendered":"Please join us at the demo!"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xdj266r x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">There has never been a more important time to take a stand and say that refugees are welcome here. Because all that it takes for evil to flourish is for good men to stand by and do nothing.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">As part of a global day of anti-racist protest, Care4Calais will be marching in solidarity alongside <a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1qq9wsj xo1l8bm\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/StandUTR\/?__cft__[0]=AZVFfwEcrvy2UHyNBMIV1Tx__J0XGzPo9V14g4AE4v4ZaxxdLMCFo7O4bdFcR23MePHcVqxSegEaL5BQ9AVlPXn62Ec6pqPfEm0nZKteqScsa1nY1sCTrswgvd2nuWXyZpeSAC41dDJq_XjLbi795cnFoTegNOXa0Cq6fC0OYAQclhS2d-09Qlm3rjNkGzJb07D3HMZvxCi98R2mIKaLFv59&amp;__tn__=kK-R\">Stand Up To Racism<\/a> and <a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1qq9wsj xo1l8bm\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/tradesunioncongress?__cft__[0]=AZVFfwEcrvy2UHyNBMIV1Tx__J0XGzPo9V14g4AE4v4ZaxxdLMCFo7O4bdFcR23MePHcVqxSegEaL5BQ9AVlPXn62Ec6pqPfEm0nZKteqScsa1nY1sCTrswgvd2nuWXyZpeSAC41dDJq_XjLbi795cnFoTegNOXa0Cq6fC0OYAQclhS2d-09Qlm3rjNkGzJb07D3HMZvxCi98R2mIKaLFv59&amp;__tn__=-]K-R\">Trades Union Congress (TUC)<\/a> in London on March 18, 2023. Demonstrations will also take place in Cardiff and Glasgow.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">This moment could be a turning point in our history, and we need to ensure that fairness prevails. As governments around the world are intensifying hostile environments for refugees and migrants, your support is needed more than ever, as we say loud and clear: Refugees are welcome here!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1qq9wsj xo1l8bm\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/hashtag\/refugeeswelcome?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZVFfwEcrvy2UHyNBMIV1Tx__J0XGzPo9V14g4AE4v4ZaxxdLMCFo7O4bdFcR23MePHcVqxSegEaL5BQ9AVlPXn62Ec6pqPfEm0nZKteqScsa1nY1sCTrswgvd2nuWXyZpeSAC41dDJq_XjLbi795cnFoTegNOXa0Cq6fC0OYAQclhS2d-09Qlm3rjNkGzJb07D3HMZvxCi98R2mIKaLFv59&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#RefugeesWelcome<\/a><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1qq9wsj xo1l8bm\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/hashtag\/noracismnofascism?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZVFfwEcrvy2UHyNBMIV1Tx__J0XGzPo9V14g4AE4v4ZaxxdLMCFo7O4bdFcR23MePHcVqxSegEaL5BQ9AVlPXn62Ec6pqPfEm0nZKteqScsa1nY1sCTrswgvd2nuWXyZpeSAC41dDJq_XjLbi795cnFoTegNOXa0Cq6fC0OYAQclhS2d-09Qlm3rjNkGzJb07D3HMZvxCi98R2mIKaLFv59&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#NoRacismNoFascism<\/a><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rn